						<ul class="space-y-1 text-sm list-disc list-inside marker:text-black">
							<li>.NET / C#</li>
							<li>Azure Infrastructure</li>
							<li>Go & HTMX</li>
							<li>React / TypeScript</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				// COLUMN 2: THE ATHLETE (Physical)
				<div class="space-y-4">
					<div class="p-4 border-2 border-black h-full">
						<h2 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 uppercase border-b-2 border-black pb-2">
							II. The Athlete
						</h2>
						<p class="text-sm mb-4 leading-snug">
							Believing in the unity of mind and body. I train daily, tracking metrics via Garmin to optimize performance.
						</p>
						
						<h3 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 mt-6">[ Current Focus ]</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-1 text-sm list-disc list-inside marker:text-black">
							<li>Strength Training</li>
							<li>Manual Labor</li>
							<li>Endurance Running</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				// COLUMN 3: THE ARTIST (Creative)
				<div class="space-y-4">
					<div class="p-4 border-2 border-black h-full">
						<h2 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 uppercase border-b-2 border-black pb-2">
							III. The Artist
						</h2>
						<p class="text-sm mb-4 leading-snug">
							Exploring the human condition through visual arts and classic literature.
						</p>
						
						<h3 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase mb-2 mt-6">[ Interests ]</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-1 text-sm list-disc list-inside marker:text-black">
							<li>Filmmaking</li>
							<li>Painting</li>
							<li>Philosophy</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>

			// EXPERIENCE SECTION
			<div class="mt-16">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 uppercase border-b-2 border-black pb-2 inline-block">Professional Experience</h2>
				
				<div class="border-l-2 border-black pl-8 space-y-10 ml-2">
					// Job 1
					<div class="relative">
						<span class="absolute -left-[39px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 bg-black"></span>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase">Software Engineer Intern</h3>
						<span class="text-sm font-bold block mb-2">[ Present ]</span>
						<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
							Building AI chatbots and data pipelines using Azure OpenAI and Document Intelligence. Implementing RAG architectures for enterprise document querying.
						</p>
					</div>

					// Job 2 (Example Placeholder)
					<div class="relative">
						<span class="absolute -left-[39px] top-1.5 w-3 h-3 border-2 border-black bg-white"></span>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase">Full Stack Developer</h3>
						<span class="text-sm font-bold block mb-2">[ 2024 - 2025 ]</span>
						<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
							Developed internal tools using .NET Core and React. Optimized SQL queries for reporting dashboards.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
